Maorihead
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:usu. <i>Carex</i> spp (esp. <i>C. secta</i> and <i>C. virgata</i>)
Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See: niggerhead
Pronunciation:
